menu "Privacy Shield Configuration"

    config PRIVACY_SHIELD_DEBUG_MODE
        bool "Debug mode (raw audio dump over serial)"
        default y
        help
            When enabled, raw microphone samples are printed to serial
            for debugging and plotting. This requires a high baud rate
            (2,000,000) on the serial monitor.

            Disable for production deployment — audio samples will be
            routed to the DSP pipeline instead.

endmenu
